Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteUninstantiatedModules(25.10)          deleteUninstantiatedModules(25.10)

Name
       deleteUninstantiatedModules - Deletes uninstantiated modules

Syntax
       deleteUninstantiatedModules

       [-help]

       [-reportOnly]

       Deletes uninstantiated modules.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man deleteUninstantiatedModules

       -reportOnly
              Reports all uninstantiated vcells instead of deleting them.

              All  uninstantiated vcells will be deleted if -reportOnly is not
              specified.

              Data_type: bool, optional

Related Information
              * ECO Flows chapter in the Innovus User Guide

